author: Marcus Cho
title: C.E.’s First Drop of SS17 Is Available Now
text:
Visit the original post to see all 10 images from this gallery. 
The rise of Cav Empt’s success has been a long time coming, and after multiple seasons of streetwear excellence and the launch of its Tokyo flagship location , they’ve proven that they’re ready to take on whatever’s ahead.
Recently, Cav Empt released their first SS17 drop, and as per usual in Cav Empt fashion, it’s full of boundary-pushing aesthetics. You’ll find pieces like the “Skyline Graphic” crewneck to be extraordinarily unique in its design; offering a bold look while maintaining the subtlety of its base silhouette. Overall, the collection features an array of cold-ready clothes perfect for immediately adding to your wardrobe.
Check out the full drop over at Cav Empt’s official site now.
